parameters.query:
SELECT 
    c.CallId,
    c.StartTime,
    c.EndTime,
    c.CallStatus,
    c.Channel,
    c.FirstName,
    c.LastName,
    c.PrimaryPhoneNum,
    c.CalledFromNumber,
    c.Notes,
    
    -- LawSubType details
    lst.LawSubTypeId,
    lst.LawSubTypeCode,
    lst.ShortDescription AS CallTypeName,
    lst.IsQualified,
    lst.LawTypeBroadId,
    lst.LawTypeNarrowId,
    
    -- MediaSource details
    ms.MediaSourceId,
    ms.MediaSourceName,
    ms.VendorGroup,
    ms.CampaignGroup,
    
    -- Company details
    co.CompanyId,
    co.ShortName AS Account,
    co.LongName AS AccountName

FROM Calls c
LEFT JOIN LawSubTypes lst ON c.CallType = lst.LawSubTypeId
LEFT JOIN MediaSources ms ON c.MediaSourceId = ms.MediaSourceId
LEFT JOIN Companies co ON c.CompanyId = co.CompanyId

WHERE {{ $json.whereClause }}

ORDER BY c.StartTime DESC
